{
  "stem": "18061.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I was growing up, I was, according to my father, I wasn't too religious, but I know the Bible.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know the Bible by heart and still up to now.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The thing is I grew up to be a Jew, a good Jew, a fair Jew, but to be a Jew.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never, never in my life thought that being in a party, like anti-religious party or a Communist Party or the Socialist Party, would give us Jews any survival or any help.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One thing we could do is we've got to have our own state.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that is the state of Israel, which since I was, I would say, 10 or 12 years, I belong to-- to the Youth Organization of the Zionist.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then I belonged to the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The name of the organization was Poale Zion, which today they don't exist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they got their name in Israel, Mapai, which the Ben-Gurion organization.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was active in that organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All the holidays, not only Shabbos, every holiday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A holiday in our house was a real holiday.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Shabbos was a special day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody went to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would dress in the best clothes, what we had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went to shul.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From the shul, we came home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We ate whatever we got.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, in the afternoon sometime, we were-- we went to cheder or we went to shul to say a special prayer.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Saturday afternoon, there's a special prayer we say-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] means how to behave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She tried to make a meal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It should be different from the whole week, if it was money-wise.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she always did something, depends on what she could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The most important thing was a cholent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What come, potatoes, meat, a bone, a little fattening.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
